In order for this program to run on windows, it requires libpdcurses.dll
The source for this is located at https://github.com/wmcbrine/PDCurses

======================
Building Instructions:
======================
$ git clone https://github.com/wmcbrine/PDCurses
$ cd PDCurses/wincon/
$ make DLL=Y
Note: If cross compiling on linux with mingw32, the Makefile will need
to be edited to include the proper commands.
$ mv pdcurses.dll libpdcurses.dll

libpdcurses.dll should then be moved to your build directory.
